## Available Features (from pyJianYingDraft API)

### Core — Mặc định bật

| Feature | Mô tả |
|---------|--------|
| **Image track** | Mỗi scene → 1 ảnh trên video track, timecode từ SRT |
| **Audio track** | Import file mp3 narration |
| **Subtitle track** | Import từ SRT file |
| **Auto Ken Burns** | Zoom nhẹ 1.0→1.05 suốt mỗi ảnh (cinematic feel) |

### Enhancement — Dropdown/Checkbox

| Feature | Options | Default |
|---------|---------|---------|
| **Transition** | Dissolve, Fade, Move Up/Down/Left/Right, Compress | Dissolve |
| **Transition duration** | 0.3s, 0.5s, 0.7s, 1.0s | 0.5s |
| **Intro animation** | Fade In, Zoom In, Zoom Out, None | Fade In |
| **Outro animation** | Fade Out, Zoom Out, None | None |
| **Background blur** | None, Level 1-4 | None |
| **Image scale mode** | Fit (letterbox), Fill (crop), Stretch | Fill |

